description: Perfectly positioned in South Boston, 8 G St offers the best of city living with unmatched proximity to downtown. This home blends classic charm with modern updates, requiring minimal finishing touches to reach its full potential. Soaring ceilings, brick accents, abundant natural light, and beautifully preserved details create a warm, inviting atmosphere. The meticulously crafted interior showcases stylish finishes while maintaining its original Boston allure. With a spacious interior and move-in ready appeal, this home is ideal for those looking to enjoy the vibrant neighborhood's dining, shopping, and waterfront/beach access. Whether you're a savvy investor or homeowner looking to enjoy city living at your doorstep, this rare property presents a number of dynamic opportunities. Don't miss this exceptional find in the heart of Southie! Seller would prefer to sell 8 G St, and 10 G St as a package deal, but are willing to sell separately.
